tags.name: Oatman-Topock Highway
tags.note: (ADOT) and Mohave installed bridge over the Sacramento Wash in Topock, Arizona providing a 110-ft clear span that will pass the 2-year, 30-minute storm event using Prefabricated Bridge Elements and Systems (PBES) for the abutments and superstructure.
Primary due to numbered national highway. Listed in Caltran's California Road System as Minor Arterial.
